--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
README Woefzela v10.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Description

The Woefzela software application supports speech data collection from different speakers using an Android device. 

Prompts are displayed and speakers guided in producing the necessary recordings. The output, consisting of audio and associated transcriptions, is typically used as training and/or testing data for building Automatic Speech Recognition (ASR) systems in the target language.

