--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Citing

If you find this application useful, please cite the associated paper:

N.J. de Vries, J. Badenhorst, M.H. Davel, E. Barnard and A. de Waal, “Woefzela - An open-source platform for ASR data collection in the developing world,” in Proc. INTERSPEECH, Florence, Italy, August 2011, pp. 3177-3180.

Nic J. de Vries, Marelie H. Davel, Jaco Badenhorst, Willem D. Basson, Febe de Wet, Etienne Barnard and Alta de Waal, “A smartphone-based ASR data collection tool for under-resourced languages”, Speech Communication, Volume 56, January 2014, pp 119-131.

